snippet.title: Alpha One // Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam, please wishlist today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1383520/Alpha_One/

Alpha One is a turn based strategy game with real time encounters. Each action level is a turn in a strategic conflict to survive or defeat your opponent. Race to collect resources, acquire upgrades, expand territory and economy, build defenses, all to defeat the enemy or escape home.
